X l gi tr =0
In[6]:
import numpy as np
columns_zero = ['Glucose','BloodPressure','SkinThickness','Insulin','BMI']
# Chuyn ct v float  c th cha NaN, sau  thay th 0 -> NaN
df[columns_zero] = df[columns_zero].astype(float).replace(0, np.nan)
# in NaN bng gi tr trung bnh ca tng ct
df[columns_zero] = df[columns_zero].fillna(df[columns_zero].mean())
print("\n-- Kim tra li s lng gi tr thiu sau khi x l: ---")
print(df.isnull().sum())
print("\n-- Thng k m t sau khi lm sch d liu: ---")
print(df.describe())

Nhn xt v phn phi cc bin:

  • Age (Tui) v Pregnancies (S ln mang thai): Phn phi lch phi, cho thy phn ln bnh nhn l ngi tr tui v c s ln mang thai t.
  • Glucose (ng huyt) v BloodPressure (Huyt p): C phn phi gn ging vi phn phi chun.
  • BMI (Ch s khi c th), DiabetesPedigreeFunction, v Insulin: Cc bin ny u c phn phi lch phi (right-skewed) r rt. ui ca biu ko di v pha cc gi tr ln, cho thy c mt s t bnh nhn c cc ch s ny rt cao

Nhn xt v Ma trn tng quan:

  • Cc cp c tng quan dng ng ch nht l:
    • Age v Pregnancies (0.54): Hp l, tui cng cao th s ln mang thai c th cng nhiu.
    • BMI v SkinThickness (0.57): Hp l, ch s khi c th thng i i vi dy lp m di da.
    • Glucose v Outcome (0.49): Mc ng huyt cao c lin quan cht ch n vic b tiu ng.
    • Glucose v Insulin (0.42): Mi quan h sinh l hc c bit n.
  • Cc mi tng quan khc u kh yu.

Nhn xt Pairplot:

  • Phn phi (ng cho): Phn phi ca ngi b bnh (mu cam) thng dch v pha bn phi (gi tr cao hn) cc bin Glucose, BMI, Age, v Pregnancies.
  • Scatter plots:
    • C th thy s phn tch r rng hn gia hai nhm Outcome khi nhn vo biu ca Glucose so vi cc bin khc.
    • Mi quan h gia Age v Pregnancies cho thy mt xu hng tng chung.

Phn tch ngoi l

In[11]:
fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 3, figsize=(18,10))
cols = ['Glucose','Age', 'BMI', 'Pregnancies', 'Insulin', 'SkinThickness']
for ax, col in zip(axes.flatten(), cols):
    sns.boxplot(x='Outcome', y=col, data=df, ax=ax)
    ax.set_title(f'Phn phi {col} theo Outcome')
    ax.set_xticks([0,1])
    ax.set_xticklabels(['Khng b bnh', 'B bnh'])
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Nhn xt Phn phi cc bin theo Outcome:

  • Glucose: Nhm ngi b bnh (Outcome=1) c mc ng huyt trung v (ng k gia hp) cao hn hn so vi nhm khng b bnh. S phn b ca nhm b bnh cng rng hn.
  • BMI & SkinThickness: C hai ch s ny u c trung v cao hn nhm ngi b bnh. C nhiu gi tr ngoi l (outliers) c hai nhm, c bit SkinThickness.
  • Age & Pregnancies: Trung v ca tui v s ln mang thai nhm b bnh u cao hn. iu ny cho thy bnh tiu ng ph bin hn nhng ngi ln tui v mang thai nhiu ln.
  • Insulin: Bin ny c s lng ln cc gi tr ngoi l, cho thy s bin thin rt ln trong nng insulin gia cc c nhn, c bit l nhng ngi mc bnh.
  • Kt lun: Cc bin Glucose, BMI, v Age dng nh l nhng yu t d bo quan trng cho vic chn on bnh tiu ng.
